data.description: Potential to assume an FHA mortgage at 2.87%. Inquire for more details.   This stunning home has been lovingly cared for abundant light creating a truly custom floorplan! Located on a spacious lot with abundant trees and room to spread out in the Deerfield neighborhood this berm style will blow you away. Surrounded by windows and greenery its open floor plan has updated kitchen cabinets, quartz countertops, an island, updated windows, fresh paint throughout, wainscoting, custom lighting and so much attention to detail. Plenty of storage in the oversize garage and additional large concrete storage room. Come check out this beauty today!  All taxes and measurements are approximate
